- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper deals with auditing machine learning models. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also possible as the paper deals with deep-learning models. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is a less likely category, but it could be relevant as the paper deals with data protection and privacy issues.
